modName: DreamBurrows Princess of The Woods Retexture
summary: A Fancy Dancy Re-Texture of SydneyBs Princess of the Woods Outfit.
descriptionHtml:
Dreamburrows Princes of the Woods Re-Texture
Author - DreamBurrow
Orignal Mesh - SydneyB

--------------------------
Description:

X\'D Hello Hello!! 

This is a re-texture I made for the Princess of the Woods Outfit!! 
By SydneyB

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18008

Update:: Finally finished re-texturing version 2.0,

All outfits have been re-textured except for the boots, daggers and belts. 
Red and Olive stockings have been left alone as well. 

A/N:: I take awful screenshots, so be sure to upload some of your own!
Also, none of my followers are up for download at this time. Please don\'t ask for their files. 
And try to keep the comments about my re-texture please, Thanks :D!

Critique and advice is always welcome! Let me know if something looks off so that I may fix it. 

Thank you to everyone who downloads! Enjoy!


Amazing feature video by MMOxReview
[youtube]zIFVbd88_PY[/youtube]

--------------------------
Installation: 

Download and install SydneyBs Princess of the Woods outfit first!!::

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18008

Then install mine.

Copy all content to the Skyrim/Data folder.

--------------------------
Uninstallation: 

Remove the following folders:

Uninstall using NMM. (Nexus Mod Manager)

Or delete the files in

Skyrim/Data/Meshes/Ashara/Prince of the Woods
and 
Skyrim/Data/Textures/Ashara/Princes of the woods

---------------------------

Known Issues:

-Lighting issues.

-Poor quality, nothing I do will ever be perfect. But I do hope you like it regardless.
---------------------------
Permissions:
DO NOT upload any of my works with out my expressed permission. Thank you. 
I do not give permissions to upload my works on Steam, whatsoever. 
---------------------------

Credits:

Bethesda - Skyrim

SydneyB - For being amazing and letting me release this re-texture
for her beautiful Princess of the Woods Outfit. 

Dimon- For UNP and creating some of the awesome meshes in this outfit. 

You- I\'d like to thank everyone for the amazing encouragement, downloads and fantastic screenshots. I try my best to make these look good for you all. Thanks for enjoying them.
